Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:04.81,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.61,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with personal thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.15,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Time constantly flows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.28,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't care about people struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:17.58,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Lelouch is happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:22.23,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Since, at the very least, he could decide how the world operates through his own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:27.53,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to give an order to anyone. \NA power that enforces absolute obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:29.44,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)}He can still rely on the Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:05.80,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:09.44,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the intervention of the Chinese Federation and the terrorist acts carried out by the Order of the Black Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.36,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,there are various instances of uproar taking place around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.71,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,However, this problem is not tied to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:17.45,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fact that your attendance is not sufficient!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.16,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good your grades are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.07,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,No matter whether you're Princess Euphemia's knight or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:24.48,CG ON,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but to repeat the grade if your attendance is not sufficient!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.39,CG ON,Teacher02,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's going to take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.04,CG ON,Teacher03,0000,0000,0000,,Think we'll finish by tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.69,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,In the end Zero was our savior, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:37.35,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Even an Eleven can become successful. Look at that Kururgi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.78,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Kyushu would have been taken away by the Chinese Federation if Zero hadn't been around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.01,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,230)}But that wasn't reported on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:45.12,CG ON,???05,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia wouldn't report that, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.60,CG ON,???06,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,230)}Anything is fine as long as there's peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:51.88,CG ON,???07,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1010)}What Kururugi is working towards is peace brought about by slavery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.38,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,The opinions in the ghetto are divided?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.30,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,They are either in favor of the support faction or the rebel faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.80,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone was surprised, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.19,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Discovering that Zero wanted to build a country...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.15,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. That's too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:04.88,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,He should have been more realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.69,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.61,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.95,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.96,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Your life will change greatly by following that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.78,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,My dream of becoming a bureaucrat might come true too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.55,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Bureaucrat? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.25,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I have dreams too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:22.04,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd most likely be abusing Refrain now if I hadn't joined the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.22,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.62,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Refrain is used... the past... even Zero's real identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:31.83,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)\i1}Even if I know that... what should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.52,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ohgi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.48,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,About what we were saying earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.47,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,We can't contact Zero, even if we want to wait for his instructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.25,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as we planned earlier, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.13,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap. Give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.20,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But information routes are essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.32,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that there are people there who want to join the Order too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:51.29,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the escape routes that Diethard planned can only be used tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.79,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:04:02.05,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The most open school festival in the Tokyo Settlement will now commence in Ashford Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.84,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The signal to begin will be the voice of this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.86,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:07.79,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.87,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.54,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Nya~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.94,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Today sure is noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.97,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:20.94,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.11,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,It's Britannian cuisine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.85,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,A farcical and controversial story:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.46,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,"Tokyo and Zero". Currently being shown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.26,CG ON,???05,0000,0000,0000,,We have Prince Clovis's photo here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:34.90,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, Sawasaki and his goons were useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.25,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,With this, quite a fair bit of the conditions have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.11,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:42.38,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,All the data concerning the emergency measures that each city is taking have already been collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People from the media?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:48.73,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90\fscy90}We have also obtained a diagram showing where the solar power panels and energy collection centers are located in each settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.06,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What about the supporter that we discussed earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.46,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I alone am more than sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've worked out about 72% of the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.20,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tohdoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:05:00.14,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90\fscy90}We have obtained a detailed layout of the territory we're aiming to capture from the television, and he's inspecting it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:04.45,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,However, he wants to check that along with the plan to make use of a large dummy with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.66,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We'll confirm it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.37,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there's something I'm late in reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.56,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,About that incident with Team Zero, Vice-Commander Ohgi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.61,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,A pinch! We are caught in a big pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.25,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? A pinch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.37,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you idling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.31,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, you're the head of the executive committee, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's proceeding fine without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, President, you're in charge of that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.57,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was only two meters last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly we need to make a pizza with a diameter of twelve meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.30,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.66,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've succeeded, it'll be the first of its type in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.23,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Just the oven and ingredients alone created a huge ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You invited a television crew over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You know that we can't show our faces, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.27,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,We have to document the record broken by the pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.40,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as you hide in the booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.28,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? President's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.27,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.35,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Rivalz, I'm done on my end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.94,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you seem to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:55.87,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Did something nice happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.25,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.64,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you're going out alone with an Eleven from the ghetto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.57,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.42,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,If you find Britannians scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.75,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:10.55,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, is this really going to help you with your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.59,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.37,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to gather information for the development plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.93,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.70,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.83,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate I should just send her to the police station instead of the hospital when possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.59,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.78,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The others will be dragged down if information about me leaks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.34,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for me to silence her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.41,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.58,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,How about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.19,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.35,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.84,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be a school teacher in the past, so I felt nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.79,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:48.12,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,There was a close friend who I knew since I was a child, but he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.97,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall realize his dream for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.60,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,That dream is quite a burden on me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.14,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.55,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,I-In? But... I'm an Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.10,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.62,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We are fairly open about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.82,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I shall lead the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.84,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute, they are our customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.53,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.42,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you wouldn't come to school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.66,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Then you did it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.96,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell anyone about my true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.38,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You are Kallen Stadtfeld now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Not Kouzuki Kallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.26,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to capture me after showing me compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.70,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I won't show you mercy if we meet on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.62,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to continue to try to convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.98,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is against the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.10,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,but in school, rather than fighting, I choose to try to convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.39,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, the truck has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.28,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The cheese is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You came to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.70,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... My physical condition wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:58.57,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen, about what we spoke of earlier, it has nothing to do with school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.79,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen, if possible, can you go to the classrom to help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be short on people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.88,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.82,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Are you frightened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.06,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Bleh, don't be scared just by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.12,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Lelouch that asshole...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.43,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a horror house, just explain that it's a horror house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:26.90,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, the only one who can order me around is Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.79,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... another couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.87,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,If they can do something like this, they might as well mechanize everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.25,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it is light, it's pretty hot wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.32,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's nearly the same as the early Glasgow models.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.41,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:40.60,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.27,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.13,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Ohgi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.03,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,You were safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.09,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.07,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The school festival sure is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.84,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,She's aiming only for him... You think he resembles Lloyd-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.06,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed harsh to leave everything to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.54,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The pizza will start in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:12.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Drama club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.40,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've already spoken to the movie society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, the preparation for the coup d'état will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.70,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.74,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It slipped out of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.62,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even soldiers? It sure is peaceful here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.10,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're Suzaku-kun's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.75,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.33,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I eat the pizza that they claim is the largest in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.67,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.51,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,To think you came back after spending just one night at Area 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.48,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,The Cornelia army sure is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.95,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.98,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, it's all because you loaned us your own personal army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.15,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.55,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Joining up with the Graston Knights that were on standby in the main country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.85,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,This allows our army to regain the prestige it should always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.32,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,The Zattel Buffer of the Glouester is ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.06,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.73,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,I will make use of that card in my negotiations with the Chinese Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.03,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:05.91,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,It's such an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:06.83,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:11.83,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,To be depended on by Princess Cornelia who is unrivaled in the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.34,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.89,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:20.39,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,In the battlefield you're much more beautiful and dazzling than any flower or butterfly at a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.71,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're like the Flash of Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.47,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.79,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Euphie's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.77,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is about to set off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.50,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie already spoke to me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.63,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.44,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.72,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, also, about that thing that Bartley is in-charge of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.66,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I don't mind. But is that thing actually useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.97,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,As I was saying, the world's largest pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I would bring some back. Stay in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.68,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pull tricks for such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Soilders and people from the media are around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do if you got caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.81,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes better when it's freshly baked from the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.27,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the disguise kit over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm now busy planning the school festival and the coup d'état...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.09,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come into the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.64,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.10,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.27,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be an Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:12.90,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.22,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.34,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:20.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.49,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This place is off-limits to unauthorized personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.58,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.58,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ohgi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.70,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.37,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that I have to tell Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.29,CG ON,001,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.46,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, I think that this idea is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.17,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.90,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for you to follow the path you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.20,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,790)}I'll try to talk to Cornelia on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:49.17,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suzaku, Brother has agreed with my thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.35,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:51.31,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.70,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.43,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be the one apologizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.23,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nunnally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:00.15,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That voice, don't tell me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.33,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn, he saw Ohgi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad. If they see C.C. here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.41,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,The gas cylinders used for the burner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.45,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the spares were placed here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.11,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:16.67,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.05,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,E-Erm... Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.50,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Are the spare cylinders there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.84,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Rivalz is looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.08,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... They might be on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:25.90,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.20,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.89,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just use the Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.46,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to use it on Ohgi and that unknown person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.40,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the rest are people that I've used it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.63,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You get what you deserve. Who asked you to use it so freely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.35,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You... Don't you understand what the current situation is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.65,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.02,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,You were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.82,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, there's something I want to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you escape alone first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.62,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of busy right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.67,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll create a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.58,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Make use of that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.32,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.25,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get to meet you except for times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.19,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.25,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the board is falling! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:03.29,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.22,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.82,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... Erm... Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.51,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.24,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a warning that gas is leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the valve has come loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:29.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, can someone help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.10,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:33.29,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I feel... a familiar sensation on my leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:36.50,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for getting you involved in such a weird incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.34,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I sort of enjoyed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.41,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've felt this excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.93,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to leave Area 11?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.76,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, the person who shot you won't be able to chase after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:55.56,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Ohgi-san... Was the previous me much happier than how I am now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:56.68,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,That is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.85,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:02.27,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Can you... continue with what you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.86,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,"She's my...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.86,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.57,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.28,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't mind becoming an Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.92,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep things about Brother and me secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:24.09,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,But if this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.30,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine as long as I get to live with Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:34.27,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the fights the two of us had back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:37.04,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Arguing who would become Brother's bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:42.56,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered saying "You must decide who would be the one tonight." And that placed Lelouch in quite a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.02,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.74,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.24,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, do you still feel the same about Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.49,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.57,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.96,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,The making of the world's largest pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:05.29,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the thing below my feet is an oven specially made for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.75,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful way of squandering the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find some time, so go to stage B to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:14.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:21.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No one will die even if there's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.81,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from you. Seems like everything will proceed on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.19,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Lately I've learned how to order people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone is really optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was only recently that the Chinese Federation came to invade us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.74,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.94,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Festivals are essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:41.74,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it is, no matter when it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.19,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,You're still naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.86,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.82,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.46,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, the pizza is... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.85,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Contact me if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:55.87,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.72,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,The preparation of the ingredients should be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.93,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, time to introduce this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.50,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,The one tossing the pizza will be the Ashford family's Ganymede!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.53,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that grand enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:12.75,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,However! The one piloting it is our student council's disciplinary member and Her Highness Euphemia's knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:16.15,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.77,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.61,CG ON,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A lot of Elevens came as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.88,CG ON,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's an open school festival and it's also the school that Suzaku-san studies in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.20,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:31.17,CG ON,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To the Elevens, Suzaku-san is the star of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.13,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:36.24,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Third generation KnightMare Ganymede.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:39.10,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Marianne, the Flash of Lightning, used this machine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:41.45,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the base frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.18,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a doll used for events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:48.64,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It's a unique machine that escaped the era of conflict that followed Queen Marianne's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.23,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,So that was indeed your aim for the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.72,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,So you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.45,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The person here is not attracted to the opposite gender at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:58.93,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I do possess the basic concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:03.52,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful! How large can he make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.75,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun, we are all anticipating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I was in charge of that last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.04,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't compare to a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Today was just filled with surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.39,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch and Nunnally were actually so near,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.62,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,and are friends with Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.05,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,What is that guy doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.35,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time to be fooling around with girls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.87,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I detest that everyone can't be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is the last time we'll ever meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:31.57,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,No, because I found a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.36,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lelou...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.45,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Princess Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.88,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Someone said "Princess Euphemia"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.32,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.17,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! It's Princess Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.54,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.48,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, take Nunnally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll do that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.38,CG ON,001,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, seems that the Vice Governor-General is near the main entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.72,CG ON,002,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'm activating the reserve team as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.04,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Camera, prepare to connect to the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.51,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.09,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Princess Euphemia came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:01.85,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.43,CG ON,???05,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.33,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,If you get pushed down...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.65,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.73,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you have left it to the pros right from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:23.61,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we have to give up on this... Due to various reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.75,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.57,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.56,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Vice Governor-General, Her Highness the third Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.92,CG ON,001,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the assistance. We'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:38.24,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from HiTV. Please say something, even one line will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.18,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia, I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.51,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Please escape this way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.67,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.39,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.92,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:55.31,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a great strategy that you're able to escape yourself, Vice-Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.68,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.53,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.24,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the hidden space of the broadcast van won't be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.59,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a need for the commander of Team Zero to escape either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:08.87,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,However, I still hope that you will continue to conceal your identity and continue acting secretly in the settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.91,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I will one day introduce you to Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.08,CG ON,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.79,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.00,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,My my my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.67,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.11,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:26.00,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What about Sister Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She's safe. Suzaku saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.35,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.77,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:36.27,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going well between Sister Euphie and Suzaku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:41.03,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them... sure match each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.83,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god they are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:57.15,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia, please give us your comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.61,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Can you broadcast this video to all of Area 11?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.09,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A live broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.22,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.14,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I have an important announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.14,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.09,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:08.52,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.31,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,She did something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.29,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We are broadcasting an emergency message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:17.65,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I am Euphemia, the Vice Governor-General of Area 11 of the Holy Imperial Britannian Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:21.92,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,There is something important that I want to announce to everyone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:25.11,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,What? The little lady is making such a big fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:33.62,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I, Euphemia Li Britannia, announce the area surrounding Fuji Mountain to be the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What? Britannia is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.09,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Acknowledging... Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.33,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:41.19,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,They actually did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.01,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a restricted region...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:49.56,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,In the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon, Elevens are again able to use the name "Japanese".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.88,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The restrictions placed on the Elevens as well as the privileges given to the Britannians
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.98,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,won't apply in the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:01.07,CG ON,Eupehmia,0000,0000,0000,,Be it Britannians or Elevens, it is a fair world for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about that case before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.88,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But that is just a dreamlike story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.33,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:14.13,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't unveil your past or your mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:17.50,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, please join the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.39,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.65,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...? What about Prince Clovis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.71,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:27.88,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, join me and together we shall create a new future from within Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:31.14,CG ON,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live Princess Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.18,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she said "Japanese"... But why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.29,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's because she has an Eleven boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.39,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:41.88,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what I choose, the Order of the Black Knights will be torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will lose its raison d'être.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't expect it to be done so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:51.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think you will obtain everything just by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even providing us with a place to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:59.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then you didn't see or hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:02.44,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a terrorist that hides his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:04.05,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.26,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lelouch, we can go back to how it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.57,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's different from how it used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.93,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.60,0:23:48.45,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.56,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If I cooperate with them, my military power will be taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:53.32,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If I rebel against them, the people will become my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:55.78,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights will collapse here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:57.45,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:24:00.36,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,the third Princess who innocently brandishes kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.13,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To Nunnally and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:05.13,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence is a sin!
